title: Global Day of Coderetreat 2013 - Lübeck, Germany
description:
We will celebreate the global day of code retreat at cloudsters (http://luebeck.cloudsters.net/) in Lübeck (http://goo.gl/maps/x3nHF), a nice location to get fresh ideas. This will be a classic code retreat with 45min sessions, game of life and other funny exercises. 
Come and join us! Please register here (https://coderetreat-hl.eventbrite.com/). Registration starts at 2013/11/04. The event is supported by Draeger (http://www.draeger.com/sites/de_de/Pages/Krankenhaus/Welcome.aspx).

 8:30 : Introduction
 9:00 : Session #1
